{"tid":2331660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《Guardians of the galaxy) 彭斯宣布 美太空軍成員定名為「守護者」","createTime":"2020-12-19T03:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T01:24:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":61,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"cf43823b6b7a36a1d750d167d19e274fa027995f","tid":2331660,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普去年成立美國第六軍種「太空軍」，建軍將滿一年之際，副總統彭斯宣布為太空軍成員定名，名稱為「守護者」（Guardians）。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，彭斯當地時間週五在白宮記者會上表示，「我很榮幸代表總統宣布，今後美國太空軍的男、女性成員會以『守護者』稱號為人所知，士兵、水手、飛行員、海軍陸戰隊和守護者將在即將到來的世代捍衛我們的國家。」<br />\n<br />\n「守護者」這個稱呼是由太空軍自行選出，在此之前都是以「太空專家」代稱。<br />\n<br />\n太空作戰部長上將雷蒙德在挑選過程中否決了像是「Airman」（飛行員）這樣的稱號，他認為性別中立的名稱對一個在2020年建立的機構有其重要性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3385915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3385915&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=16814a26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3385915&h=7cbede2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3385915</a>"},{"pid":"1c9c60df8fda8c7891f0ddccdb54fb17313383c2","tid":2331660,"uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"咁其他三軍叫咩名？"},{"pid":"15925f7dc3ba5d7e923ef585805cf56378b0cd3d","tid":2331660,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"Destiny"},{"pid":"a3e0341fc62b0c3dc84d66a21531c6a6be7f0596","tid":2331660,"uid":174060,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imEhecV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimEhecV.gif&h=d486c050&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8829b06338d880bc37df4acc6021a7a42617d6b","tid":2331660,"uid":345137,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"1c9c60df